						<p>I like the idea of students writing wikipedia articles. The only drawback is that the quality would almost certainly drop, since these students would actually be training their skills on a public encyclopaedia instead of in the privacy of their own classroom where errors are hidden from our eyes. <img src='http://markos.gaivo.net/blog/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
